<!DOCTYPE topic PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Topic//EN" "topic.dtd">
<topic id="webauthor-embed-custom-action">
    <title>Embedding a Custom Action in the Web Author Interface</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Embedding a custom action in the Web Author UI</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
    <body>
        <p>You can control your workflow and provide custom functionality by embedding a custom
      action in a <term>Web Author</term> toolbar, contextual menu, or form control. For example,
      you could create an action that checks a file in or out of a file repository, or an action
      that marks the file as being reviewed.</p>
    <p>To embed a custom action:<ol>
        <li><xref href="customizing_plugins.dita#customizing_plugins">Create a plugin for Web
            Author</xref>.</li>
        <li>Use the <term>Oxygen</term> JavaScript API to <xref keyref="jscript_api_customaction"
            >implement a custom action</xref> and add it in the <term>Web Author</term>
          interface.</li>
      </ol></p>
    </body>
</topic>
